OL,3,CTim Burgess and Lisa Stanfield to be
OL,4,Chonoured at Northern Music Awards
OL,6,FMusical icons from across the North
OL,7,FWest are set to be honoured alongside
OL,8,Fup and coming acts at the first ever
OL,9,FNorthern Music Awards.
OL,11,FThe new award show, which will be held
OL,12,Fat Manchester's Albert Hall on 23
OL,13,FApril, aims to celebrate iconic
OL,14,Fnorthern bands, venues, and festivals
OL,15,Fwhile raising money for charity.
