OL,3,CTim Burgess and Lisa Stanfield to be
OL,4,Chonoured at Northern Music Awards
OL,6,FThe Charlatans front man Tim Burgess,
OL,7,Ffrom Worsley, will be presented with
OL,8,Fthe Northern Music Award 2024 for all
OL,9,Fof his work over his 30 year career,
OL,10,Fincluding 18 albums and 17 top 30
OL,11,Fsingles.
OL,13,FTim Burgess said: "It's incredible to
OL,14,Fbe recognised with the inaugural
OL,15,FNorthern Music Award. Music is
OL,16,Fimportant on so many levels, and I'm a
OL,17,Ffirm believer in the unique way that
OL,18,Fit can connect people."
