OL,3,CTim Burgess and Lisa Stanfield to be
OL,4,Chonoured at Northern Music Awards
OL,6,FAlongside Tim Burgess, Manchester-born
OL,7,Fsinger-songwriter Lisa Stansfield will
OL,8,Freceive the Northern Icon Award.
OL,10,FMoney raised from ticket sales and on
OL,11,Fthe night will go towards organisers
OL,12,FNordoff and Robbins' plan to build a
OL,13,Fstat of the art music therapy centre
OL,14,Fin Salford.
OL,16,FThe new space will employ trained
OL,17,Fmusic therapists to help support those
OL,18,Fsuffering with life-limiting
OL,19,Fillnesses, disability, and social
OL,20,Fisolation.
