OL,3,CTim Burgess and Lisa Stanfield to be
OL,4,Chonoured at Northern Music Awards
OL,6,FNadra Shah, Director of Engagement and
OL,7,FCommunications for Nordoff and
OL,8,FRobbins, said: "The Northern Music
OL,9,FAwards is a chance for us to shine a
OL,10,Flight on those who work tirelessly to
OL,11,Fmake sure live music is available and
OL,12,Faccessible throughout the North of
OL,13,FEngland.
OL,15,F"We are excited to honour some of the
OL,16,Findustry's much loved venues and
OL,17,Ffestivals alongside an array of live
OL,18,Fperformances and appearances from some
OL,19,Fof the most celebrated artists from
OL,20,Fthe region."
